    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue trinitatis. <persName
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Emperor/king" ref="#people/7"
                            >Otto</persName> divina favente misericordia Romanorum <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Iam dudum omnia quae data
                        sunt <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/81"
                            key="#Chancellor #Dioecesis #Plebs #Districtio #Mother_churches #Bishops #Archpriests"
                            >sancto Eusebio</orgName> confirmavimus, sed ea que sunt necessaria et
                        maxime ea que <persName ref="#people/32" key="#Emperor/king"
                            >Karulus</persName> imperator <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/33"
                            >Lituardo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs> aut dedit aut reddidit, iterum et iterum ex
                        nunc confirmamus et successores nostros idem agere rogamus, quia nos ipsi
                        imperatoris Karuli. <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">precepta</rs> legimus
                        et litere in <rs key="#Mother_churches">ecclesia</rs> sancti Eusebii a
                        tempore Karuli super altare sancti Iohannis baptiste scripte testimonium
                        donant et ad veritatem recognoscendam fidem legentibus faciunt, id est <rs
                            key="#Teloneum">toloneum</rs> et <rs key="#Districtio">districtum</rs>
                        suarum <rs key="#Plebs">plebium</rs> et super sua <rs key="#Casali"
                            >habitancium</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers #Fluvial_transport">aquam de
                            Scicida</rs>, aquam de Saruo, aquam de Eleuo cum utrisque ripis a loco
                        ubi nascuntur, usque in Padum, aquam de Pado cum duabus rippis a
                            <placeName>Lionna</placeName> usque <orgName key="#Plebs">plebem
                            Martori</orgName>, aquam de Duria cum utrisque ripis a <placeName>Petra
                            grossa </placeName>usque<placeName ref="#places/183"
                            >Verucham.</placeName> Confirmamus <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Malascum</placeName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/96"><placeName ref="#places/99"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Firminianam</placeName></geogName>, <placeName ref="#places/51"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><geogName ref="#estates/63"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Sestignum</geogName></placeName>, <geogName ref="#estates/41"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/3"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Carexianam</placeName></geogName> cum utraque ripa, <placeName
                            ref="#places/50"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle"
                                ref="#estates/62">Buiellam</geogName></placeName> cum omnibus suis
                        appendiciis, <placeName ref="#places/206"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Galianicum</placeName><placeName ref="#places/208"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Ponderanam</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Mulinariam</placeName>, <placeName ref="#places/210"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Mention #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Andornum</placeName>, <placeName>Causades</placeName>, montem
                            <placeName ref="#places/211">Cisidola</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Pedroro</placeName>, <placeName>Blatini</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Beduluum</placeName> et <placeName ref="#places/212"
                            >Clauaziam</placeName>, <placeName ref="#places/213">Candele</placeName>
                        et <placeName ref="#places/214">Cliuoli</placeName> quia <persName
                            ref="#people/21" key="#Emperor/king">Berengarius</persName> et
                            <persName>Albertus</persName> reges quorum <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >proprietates</rs> fuerunt, ei dederunt, <placeName ref="#places/215"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Treuerem</placeName> et districtum per totum Buiellensem et
                            <placeName>Calaniago</placeName>, <placeName>Redigada</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Readigadella</placeName>, <placeName>Trebledo</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Orco</placeName>, vallem <placeName ref="#places/103"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Cledi</placeName>, <placeName key="#Gualdi">Walda</placeName>. Damus
                        omnia predia <persName>Ardoini</persName> filii
                            <persName>Daidonis</persName>, quia hostis publicus adiudicatus
                        episcopum <persName>Petrum</persName>
                        <placeName>Vercellensem</placeName> interfecit et interfectum incendere non
                        expavit, et predia eorum qui exploratu armis et ipsis manibus huic
                        crudelitati interfuerunt, id est filiorum <persName>Teperti</persName> de
                            <placeName>Cassale</placeName>
                        <persName>Goslini</persName>, <persName>Aimini</persName> de
                            <placeName>Liuurno</placeName>, <persName>Alberti</persName> et
                            <persName>Gribaldi</persName> de <placeName>Vnglano</placeName>. Damus
                        predia illorum qui cum armis ecclesiam sancti Eusebii vastaverunt, id est
                            <persName>Olrici</persName> de <placeName>Bayna</placeName>,
                            <persName>Roderardi</persName> de <placeName>Sandiliano</placeName>,
                            <persName>Arderici</persName> de <placeName>Magnanigulo</placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Slave">servi</rs> sancti Eusebii, <persName>Alberti</persName> et
                            <persName>Vilielmi</persName> de <placeName>Saluciola</placeName>,
                            <persName>Astulfi</persName> et fratrum eius de
                            <placeName>Vualdingo</placeName>, <persName>Vghonis</persName> de
                            <placeName>Palestre</placeName>, Stephani de Cliuolo, Ademari de
                        Gambolade, Vgonis de Ciriago, Aldonis de Leuriana, Ysac et fratris eius.
                        Confirmamus <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/127"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/216">Sulciam</placeName></geogName> cum <geogName
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Mention #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/184"><genName><placeName ref="#places/404"
                                    key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Mention #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >silva Salsa</placeName></genName></geogName>, <rs key="#Castle"
                            >castellum</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle">Uictimuli</placeName>, <rs key="#Local_markets"
                            >mercatum</rs> et districtum <orgName key="#Subdeacons">plebis
                                <placeName key="#Local_markets #Districtio" ref="#places/237">sancte
                                Aghate</placeName></orgName> et <rs key="#Curtes">curtis</rs> de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/97"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/101">Asiliano</placeName></geogName> et in
                            <placeName>Tronciano</placeName> et in altero <placeName
                            ref="#places/218"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Tronziano</placeName> et per totam campaniam et castrum <placeName
                            key="#Castle" ref="#places/218">Quirini</placeName>. Damus predia
                            <persName key="#Subdeacons">Agadi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">subdiaconi</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/400">sancta
                            Aghata</placeName>, <persName>Goslini</persName>,
                            <persName>Constancii</persName>, <persName>Guidonis</persName>,
                            <persName>Eurardi</persName>, <persName>Amizonis</persName> fratris
                            <persName>Gunterii</persName>. Confirmamus sanctam Mariam Moliade que
                        dicitur <placeName>Monasteriolum</placeName>, cum sua pertinentia, cum
                            <placeName ref="#places/219"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Bornade</placeName> et <placeName>Grignasco</placeName> et
                            <rs>districtu</rs>
                        <placeName>vallis Scicide</placeName> et <rs>erimannos</rs> de
                            <placeName>Nauola</placeName> et de Cassaliclo et <placeName
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/96">sciluam Rouaxindam</placeName>; damus <placeName
                            ref="#places/220"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Districtio"
                            >Gatinariam</placeName> cum districtu et omnia predia <persName
                            key="#Archdeacons">Gisalberti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Archdeacons">archidiaconi</rs> Vercellensis, et hoc iuste quia,
                        cum esset de familia sancti Eusebii, inflatus divitiis ecclesie ecclesiam
                        Vercellensem dominam suam fugit eamque cum <persName ref="#people/172"
                            >Ardoino</persName> miserabiliter vastavit; similiter damus predia
                        suorum generorum, id est <persName>Vuilimanni </persName>de <placeName
                            ref="#places/221">Causade </placeName>et <persName>Vgonis</persName> de
                            <placeName>Rade</placeName> et predia parentum eius servorum
                        fugitivorum, id est <persName>Liprandi</persName> et
                            <persName>Hermanni</persName> fratrum et <persName>Giselberti</persName>
                        iudicis. Districtum et teloneum in <placeName key="#Teloneum #Districtio"
                            >Rade</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Teloneum #Districtio"
                            ref="#places/222">Gislaringo</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Teloneum #Districtio"
                            ref="#places/223">Arbori</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Teloneum #Districtio" ref="#places/226"><placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Teloneum #Districtio"
                                ref="#places/224">Gregi</placeName></placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Teloneum #Districtio"
                            ref="#places/225">Albano</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Teloneum #Districtio">Conflencia</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Districtio"
                            ref="#places/227">Odonicum</placeName> cum districtu reddimus et
                            <orgName key="#Churches">ecclesiam sancti Salvatoris </orgName>ultra
                        Padum sicut Karulus augustus fecit, confirmamus. Montem Pedogletum et
                            <placeName>Brosule</placeName> et districtum in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Districtio"
                            ref="#places/228">Palazolo</placeName>, <placeName key="#Districtio"
                            >Gorzano</placeName>, <placeName key="#Districtio">Liuagi</placeName>,
                            <placeName key="#Districtio">Gabiano</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Districtio">Cantauenna</placeName>, <placeName key="#Districtio"
                            >Carderisi</placeName>, <placeName key="#Districtio"
                            >Vliaco</placeName>,<placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Districtio"
                            ref="#places/229">Malione</placeName>, <placeName key="#Districtio"
                            >Azellii</placeName>, <placeName key="#Districtio">Medule</placeName>,
                            <placeName key="#Districtio">Herbara</placeName> confirmamus. Districtum
                            <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Districtio"
                            ref="#places/230">sancti Euaxii </placeName>a Pado usque in Sturam, in
                            <placeName key="#Districtio">Fraxaneto</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Districtio">Paxiliano</placeName>, Ticinesse, <placeName
                            key="#Districtio">Sarmaza</placeName> et<placeName key="#Districtio">
                            sancto Georgio</placeName> et in <placeName key="#Districtio"
                            >Ozano</placeName> ultra tria miliaria, predia
                            <persName>Alberici</persName> de Monterone, <persName>Milonis</persName>
                        de Salerana, <persName>Tedisi </persName>de Lauagna,
                            <persName>Disonis</persName> de Vacaria, <persName>Hermanni</persName>
                        iudicis <persName>Graseuerti</persName> de Cirisudo et fratrum eius,
                        Cerrocaualli, castellum <placeName key="#Castle">sancti Angeli</placeName>
                        in Lacu maiore,<orgName key="#Monasteries"> abbaciam de <placeName
                                ref="#places/330">Arona</placeName>
                        </orgName>confirmamus sicut preceptum Karuli testatur; <placeName
                            ref="#places/231">Cerretum</placeName>, <placeName>Vulpara</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Cassanoua</placeName>, curticellem in <placeName>Bremide
                        </placeName>confirmamus, quia propria fuerunt Albani servi sancti Eusebii de
                        plebe Buiella; cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/128">Torcelli</geogName> confirmamus sicut <persName
                            ref="#people/12" key="#Emperor/king">Liprandus</persName> rex donavit;
                        cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/129">Canauam</geogName> reddimus sicuti <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king">Ludouicus</persName> imperator donavit. Damus autem
                        sancto Eusebio omnia predia <persName key="#Archpriests"
                            >Cuniberti</persName> archipresbiteri et hoc iuste et rationabiliter,
                        quia omnia que de bonis ecclesie exierunt, iudicio ecclesie et seculi ad
                        ecclesiam cuius fuerunt, pertinebunt. Confirmamus sancto Eusebio abbaciam de
                        Luceio sicuti Karulus augustus et dive memorie genitor noster fecerunt;
                        confirmamus <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/107">sancto
                            Michaeli de <placeName ref="#places/328" key="#Monasteries"
                                >Loceio</placeName></orgName> hanc pertinenciam quam Ortum sancti
                        Michaelis vocamus, id est a Monte regis usque Aquam nigram sicut currit
                        Ampori, et usque Solarium arsum et usque fossatum Axinarium et sicut est
                            <orgName>ecclesia sancte Marie </orgName>a Ponte et Stura currit subtus
                        Broilum vetus; confirmamus <placeName>Aleram</placeName> usque Gardinam et
                        usque Ronchum sichum et a Terra monacorum sicut Ampori tenet, usque in caput
                        montis Salacesse et usque in Padum; confirmamus
                            <placeName>Camassa</placeName> nigra et totum Versare usque in Ampori et
                        totum Andolinum intra Duriam et Padum et Zebadasco; confirmamus sancto
                        Michaeli de Lozaio sicut <persName ref="#people/9" key="#Emperor/king"
                            >Lotarius</persName> augustus donavit, quando corpus sancti Ianuarii ibi
                        collocavit, cortem<geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fluvial_transport #Teloneum #Districtio"
                            > Guadradula </geogName>cum districtu herimannorum et teloneo et aquam
                        Padi a portu Cleuasi cum utrisque rippis usque ad Clerum ubi vetus Duria
                        intrat in Padum et a Clero usque Mundine et Marnunca, scilvam de Loceio et
                            <placeName>Ronchum sichum</placeName> et
                            <placeName>Conzuningun</placeName> et scilvam <placeName key="#Forests"
                            >Palazolascam</placeName> confirmamus sancto Eusebio sicut ab antiquis
                        semper pertinuit. Confirmamus <geogName ref="#estates/88"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Romanianum</geogName>, <geogName ref="#estates/98"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Aucimianum</geogName> sicut Karulus augustus donavit et confirmavit.
                        Quod ut credatur et conservetur, hoc preceptum manu nostra firmavimus et
                        amore <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/171">Leonis</persName> episcopi
                        qui nobis fidei testimonio aureus est, aureo sigillo nostro iussimus
                        insigniri. Signum domni Ottonis gloriosissimi (M.) Romanorum imperatoris
                        augusti. <persName>Heribertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">canzellarius</rs> vice Petri Cumani episcopi et
                        archicanzellarii recognovit. Data non. maii anno dominice incarnationis
                        DCCCCXCVIIII, indictione XII, anno tercii Ottonis regnantis XV, imperii III;
                        actum Rome; feliciter amen. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
